It should be positioned below or alongside the cloud and book graphic, depending on the layout of the logo. The book should be open at a slight angle, with one of its pages slightly curved, as if it is ready for someone to start reading. A pen or pencil should be positioned near the book, suggesting the idea of taking notes and learning. The cloud should be positioned slightly behind the book and should appear to have a subtle shadow, as if it is floating in the background. The cloud should also have a slightly three-dimensional appearance, with its shape and texture appearing as if it could be touched and felt. The image should have an ultra-realistic quality, with detailed highlights and shadows, and a sense of depth and space. The colors used should be harmonious and complementary, with a subdued, naturalistic palette being ideal. The logo should be created in a vector format, with a high-resolution raster image also being produced for use in digital media.
